title: DJ HARRY OTTO - Karatestrike Mix 33 - August 2013
description:
THE BEST DJ HARRY OTTO MIX TO DATE.13

13 Tracks designed to run straight through your playlist. About 148bpm.

Another great mix taken from the signature Equinox Karatestrike class developed by Harry Otto. 

Amazingly clean 128count mixing is great for dance & fitness choreography. 

Again, please seed so everyone can enjoy.
